show.description: After a painful divorce shatters her quiet domestic life, Natasha reinvents herself as the bold and brilliant CEO of a rising startup. As she battles betrayal, fierce rivals, and her own inner doubts, Natasha’s journey from heartbreak to boardroom power becomes a stirring tale of grit, ambition, and transformation.
